opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 27th day of May, 2009, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the “Petition for Lack of Subject Matter Jurisdiction” and the Application for an Immediate Hearing are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
